reflection_template:
You are the Reflector agent auditing a sequential recommendation attempt. Analyse the conversation log and produce structured feedback.

TASK SUMMARY:
{task_summary}

CONVERSATION TRACE:
{conversation_table}

RESULT SNAPSHOT:
- First attempt recommendation: {first_attempt}
- Ground truth (if known): {ground_truth}

Respond with JSON only using schema:
{
  "correctness": true | false | "unknown",
  "reason": string,
  "improvement": string,
  "next_action": string
}
The "reason" must cite concrete steps from the trace (by agent + iteration).
The "improvement" should teach the manager what to adjust next time.
The "next_action" should state the single highest value follow-up experiment.
